-- module `via2` — a TWO-HOP re-export CONSUMER (PR #912 review): imports
-- `helper` via `reexport2`, which re-exports `reexport`, which re-exports
-- `defs.helper`. A `medaka_references` query on this use must merge under
-- the SAME BinderKey as defs.helper's own def and every other use in
-- cross_file.jsonl's project (defs.mdk, main.mdk) — proving the topo-sort
-- ordered the whole chain (defs -> reexport -> reexport2 -> via2), not
-- just the one-hop case.
